---
source: src/eval/runner.rs
assertion: eval commands use deterministic fixtures and metrics
schema:
  fixture: ee.eval_fixture.v1
  source_memory: ee.eval_source_memory.v1
  report: ee.eval.report.v1
contracts:
  - eval list enumerates fixtures from tests/fixtures/eval/
  - eval run loads scenario.json and source_memory.json per fixture
  - same fixture yields byte-identical JSON report
  - precision_at_k, ndcg_at_k, mrr computed for each query
  - missing fixture returns clear error with repair hint
  - malformed fixture returns parse error with path
evidence:
  - FixtureScenario.fixture_id
  - FixtureScenario.journey
  - SourceMemory.memory_id
  - EvalRunReport.metrics
  - EvalRunReport.data_hash
